{"tid":1750834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果真係贏唔到  我打賭香港人會...","createTime":"2019-11-24T14:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T14:58:46.000Z","uid":60293,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9da1268dead770f22a0861aa5ebfd5bbe2950fba","tid":1750834,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:02:41.000Z","msg":"繼續返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為好多人將希望放咗係今晚 覺得只要選到心水人選就可以解決問題<br />\n而如果輸咗  大家又會覺得冇辦法 因為今次的確係大家一人一票投出黎（好多人無視種票）<br />\n所以都唔會想出黎抗爭 因為出師無名 只會俾人覺得輸咗又唔憤氣 更加會俾黑警大造話題<br />\n<br />\n強烈請求大家一定要諗對策同調整心理 做好最壞打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d3ee589482457e421a8c5fcc5aba51b3eecc26","tid":1750834,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7a4c51a07e3b9054bb08c230d7362456f90ca3","tid":1750834,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:07:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605b491a13eb288de9d24e3093a86c1633088165","tid":1750834,"uid":286771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"調轉黎講咪得<br />\n贏左民意未退 大家明白自己做嘅野都有人支持 會更加努力爭取五大訴求<br />\n輸左即係選舉舞弊問題嚴重 無法反映真實民情 大家要更加努力推翻呢個垃圾政權<br />\n簡單黎講 輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要贏係要賴地硬架啦 唔係可以點?"},{"pid":"2815889c8f80eba837499b4d5e7980521c8be147","tid":1750834,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T14:08:06.000Z","msg":"而如何贏咗的話 更加要持續抗爭 救埋poly淨低既手足出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c70aa17bf125b007af190e6473480316fcccbe6","tid":1750834,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"605b491a13eb288de9d24e3093a86c1633088165","tid":1750834,"uid":286771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyT